{"tid":1808310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駕貨VAN失控鏟上行人路1死1傷 82歲教車師傅危駕被捕","createTime":"2020-01-02T09:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T02:14:47.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d644cce168cbb34263895365b06301316d6ed932","tid":1808310,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:41:18.000Z","msg":"【15:56】事件中姓林（53歲）男傷者送院搶救後不治。82歲教車師傅涉危險駕駛導致他人死亡被捕。<br />\n<br />\n油塘發生奪命車禍，中午約12時，一名82歲的教車師傅教畢學生後，駕駛客貨車將學生送到油塘高安里下車。師傅隨後駕車沿茶果嶺道西行落斜，不料突然失控，掃毀路中工程水馬，撞到兩名男途人，然後越過對面線，鏟上油塘站對開行人路，撞毀鐵欄再撼樓梯底的牆角始停下。<br />\n<br />\n兩名男途人分別姓林（53歲）及姓鄭（46歲），當中林半昏迷、鄭則清醒送院，據知他們是同事關係，當時前後腳過馬路。現場留下大灘血迹，二人由救護車送聯合醫院救治。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場調查，姓黃（82歲）教車師傅報稱機件故障，無法煞車；他被帶上警車問話後表示不適要求送院。肇事客貨車的「學」牌已經反轉，亦沒有任何乘客，換言之當時是正常的駕駛狀態，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉事黃姓教車師傅，既有私人教授客貨車，又有在駕駛學校掛單教私家車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200102/large/1577943650_8735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200102%2Flarge%2F1577943650_8735.jpg&h=1f0b63fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200102/60442385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60442385&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f2ad2546\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60442385&h=7d61f170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200102/60442385</a>"},{"pid":"172749f2ac2a95f401458f00dace0742147fcbe2","tid":1808310,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"死廢老又害人 仲好意思話自己係教車師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76298f2d80bb3bea47d0e5bc694aa1865b389337","tid":1808310,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"死果個係咪藍絲？"},{"pid":"bb531bb89007b51c0476a9727b742d77b6d2fedb","tid":1808310,"uid":2736,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b4608b2b85e356a876a39949f137646756f8578","tid":1808310,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb531bb89007b51c0476a9727b742d77b6d2fedb","tid":1808310,"uid":2736,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"根本就應該收返佢個教練牌啦，咁大年紀仲俾佢教而家咪出事囉"},{"pid":"834024f89b532a6583b570b4dd802a5cc2b783db","tid":1808310,"uid":77221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"想當年我個教車師傅都好老，7,80 歳左右，成日喺我揸車時恰眼瞓，好彩我都揸得熟，無事發生過。不過佢好似都退咗休嚕"},{"pid":"a1a3e9769bfe3585f14984b7dfcb0d8f49dca0aa","tid":1808310,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"76298f2d80bb3bea47d0e5bc694aa1865b389337","tid":1808310,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"死果個係咪藍絲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:17:53.000Z","msg":"求神拜佛都要係港豬藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dee6fbac484906feb09d89a736d708401608bb","tid":1808310,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:24:27.000Z","msg":"油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033bc5bccff87e222b7ad3c8a84472deea552736","tid":1808310,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"我睇條片唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n有水馬佢唔撚撞<br />\n<br />\n到中間行人路有人佢即扭軚撞落去"},{"pid":"0da12cfc7a57ce9480df8a340f63ea6b45aa9269","tid":1808310,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033bc5bccff87e222b7ad3c8a84472deea552736","tid":1808310,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02